dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Oneida County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Oneida_PLSS_2018.gdb.[Direct observation of PLSS corners with survey grade GPS by various contractors.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [To establish tighter control points for Public Land Survey System section corners.]
